Hi Everyone!

The form
<https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1bffkr2oqrMSeri2p5Bcj4Hzqeyz-NYlUndfPvN_U-DE/edit?ts=57ea7dda>for
registering for Game of Chow, in collaboration with Informals Club is out!

*https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5rUF-oDP52YbAquvrXOVK55B3EOPGb7eTTpGsEEtGSu0S2g/viewform
<https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5rUF-oDP52YbAquvrXOVK55B3EOPGb7eTTpGsEEtGSu0S2g/viewform>*

Please note the following points about the Competition :


1. There will be* 8 teams *(comprising of 2 students) selected from the
list, based on first come first serve basis.

2. We will send out the list of selected students on Friday, 30th Sep at 9
am. *Please acknowledge your selection by 9 pm, Friday on the same email
thread. *In the occasion of the team failing to acknowledge by 9 p.m. on
Friday, the next wait-listed team will be chosen.

3. There will be a short 15 min quiz before the competition starts. This
will be non-evaluative (for fun!)

4. The Club will purchase all the ingredients mentioned in the recipe, and
will be in touch with the teams regarding specific details. Teams are
reminded that they are allowed to only use ingredients and equipment given
to them by the Club.

